BARNEY: <i>Oh, boy, it's the creepy,</i>

00:08.330 --> 00:10.963
bug-eyed minister
from that culty church

00:10.965 --> 00:13.433
who kept asking us
if we're "pure enough to die."

00:13.435 --> 00:15.235
He's our best lead.
I should get this.

00:15.237 --> 00:17.854
James, unless
you have a minister,

00:17.856 --> 00:19.639
