00:19.641 --> 00:21.407
You mean, like this one?

00:21.409 --> 00:23.159
NARRATOR:
<i>A few years back,</i>

00:23.161 --> 00:27.080
<i>Barney's brother James finally</i>
<i>met his long-lost father, Sam,</i>

00:27.082 --> 00:29.082
<i>who turned out</i>
<i>to be a reverend.</i>

00:29.084 --> 00:32.317
I know pronounce
your asses saved.

00:32.320 --> 00:34.003
Whoa!

00:34.005 --> 00:37.440
NARRATOR: <i>Reverend Gibbs wouldn't be</i>
<i>the only VIP arrival that day.</i>

00:37.442 --> 00:38.925
BARNEY:
Dad!

00:38.927 --> 00:41.845
