03:51.598 --> 03:55.149
Scottish-identical-
twin-brothers style?

03:55.901 --> 03:57.401
♪ When I wake up

03:57.403 --> 03:59.854
(Scottish accent):
♪ Yeah, I know I'm gonna be ♪

03:59.856 --> 04:02.823
♪ I'm gonna be the man
who ends up next to you... ♪

04:02.825 --> 04:05.743
Oh, man, I hope they're not
singing to the same girl.

04:05.745 --> 04:07.695
Or to each other.

04:07.697 --> 04:10.114
Shut up! Music sucks!

04:10.116 --> 04:12.566
Scotland sucks! You suck!

04:12.568 --> 04:15.586
Just drive, pumpkin head.

04:15.588 --> 04:17.538
BARNEY:
Hey, guys, don't worry.

04:17.540 --> 04:18.589
Help's on the way.

04:18.591 --> 04:20.541
Oh! Thank you, Barney.
Thank you, honey.

04:20.543 --> 04:21.841
In the meantime,

04:21.844 --> 04:23.911
I'll try to keep you two
as comfortable as possible.

04:23.913 --> 04:25.846
(R&B music playing)
♪ I said, bang...

04:25.848 --> 04:27.598
Well, we don't need wine.

04:27.600 --> 04:29.767
