with it! ♪

08:31.971 --> 08:32.970
(scoffs)

08:32.972 --> 08:34.972
That's completely insane.

08:34.974 --> 08:36.924
This is how
it's gonna be.

08:36.926 --> 08:40.878
♪ We're reunited
and I'm feeling so glad ♪

08:40.880 --> 08:43.597
♪ I'm so much sexier
than Barney's dad ♪

08:43.599 --> 08:44.932
(plays flourish)

08:44.934 --> 08:48.436
♪ Back together, now
our life's right on track ♪

08:48.438 --> 08:51.856
♪ But she's banging my dad
behind your dad's back ♪

08:51.858 --> 08:56.143
♪ When you're at work,
I'm all over her rack ♪

08:56.145 --> 08:58.095
♪ That's not true ♪
♪ Yes, it is

08:58.097 --> 08:59.280
♪ That's not funny ♪

08:59.282 --> 09:00.765
♪ Mom, break the news

09:00.767 --> 09:03.334
♪ Okay, we're screwin'
like bunnies ♪

09:03.336 --> 09:04.535
♪ I'll kick your ass ♪

09:04.537 --> 09:06.820
♪ I'd like to
see you try ♪

09:06.822 --> 09:09.840
♪ Well, my dad would win
in a fight ♪

09:09.842 --> 09:13.327
♪ No, my dad would win
in a fight ♪

09:13.329 --> 09:14.345
♪ No
♪ Yeah

09:14.347 --> 09:15.629
♪ My dad would win
♪ Yeah

09:15.631 --> 09:17.765
♪ In a fight
♪ Yeah!

09:17.767 --> 09:20.000
No, my dad would win in a fight!
Nuh-uh!

09:20.002 --> 09:22.169
Uh-huh!
Don't fight!

09:22.171 --> 09:24.004
I'm marrying into this family.
BARNEY: Stop.

09:24.006 --> 09:25.856
You stupid!
I won't stop.

09:27.692 --> 09:29.977
Where the heck is
this parasailing place?

09:29.979 --> 09:31.195
(laughs)
You know what?

09:31.197 --> 09:32.863
I'm gonna...
I'm gonna call Jerry.

09:32.865 --> 09:34.198
(beep)

09:34.200 --> 09:35.366
Oh, that's weird.

09:35.368 --> 09:37.201
I just lost cell reception.

09:37.203 --> 09:39.036
Yes.

09:39.038 --> 09:41.622
Weird.

09:42.908 --> 09:46.327
Lot of pretty paintings
in this hotel.

09:46.329 --> 09:48.462
I like how
they've been... framed.

09:48.464 --> 09:51.081
I've noticed
the vintage, antique,

09:51.083 --> 09:52.633
gilded Victorian frames, too.

09:52.635 --> 09:55.719
I'm not blind...
but what are you getting at?

09:55.721 --> 09:57.354
You know damn well
what I'm getting at!

09:57.356 --> 09:59.223
You're jealous I got
the Best Mansmanship back,

09:59.225 --> 10:01.542
<i>so you destroyed that photo as</i>
<i>part of some diabolical scheme</i>

10:01.544 --> 10:03.427
<i>to make me look bad.</i>

10:03.429 --> 10:05.346
<i>I bet you even found some other</i>
<i>photo of Wayne Gretzky</i>

10:05.348 --> 10:06.514
so you could swoop in
and save the day.

10:06.516 --> 10:07.848
You're insane.
Am I?

10:07.850 --> 10:08.983
Yeah. Yeah.
Am I?

10:08.985 --> 10:11.735
Where were you today
at 3:15 p.m.?

10:11.737 --> 10:13.904
Right here
getting a massage.

10:13.906 --> 10:16.190
Rocked a 60-minute
deep tish.

10:16.192 --> 10:18.108
Now if you'll excuse
me, Detective,

10:18.110 --> 10:20.227
I think I'll go
have some pineapple.

10:21.580 --> 10:22.746
How do you know about that?

10:22.748 --> 10:25.032
Everybody knows about that!

10:25.951 --> 10:28.169
Excuse me?
Mm?

10:28.171 --> 10:29.920
You destroyed that photo,
didn't you?

10:29.922 --> 10:31.071
No, I didn't.

10:31.073 --> 10:32.406
Admit it! I complained about you

10:32.408 --> 10:34.875
to the bell captain,
so you got your revenge.

10:34.877 --> 10:36.544
You complained about me?

10:37.362 --> 10:40.047
No.

10:42.133 --> 10:44.101
So, Claude...

10:44.103 --> 10:46.387
I see that you're
a Montreal Canadiens fan.

10:46.389 --> 10:49.390
Which means you hate
the Edmonton Oilers,

10:49.392 --> 10:51.559
which is why you destroyed
the Wayne Gretzky head shot!

10:51.561 --> 10:52.643
<i>J'accuse!</i>

10:52.645 --> 10:54.428
<i>C'est ridicule!</i>

10:54.430 --> 10:55.980
If it's so <i>ridicule,</i>

10:55.982 --> 10:58.983
how do you explain this?

10:58.985 --> 11:00.818
Ah, seems
like I've caught you...

11:00.820 --> 11:03.437
midnight blue-handed.

11:03.439 --> 11:04.955
Oh, these.
Yeah.

11:04.957 --> 11:07.575
I-I was out by the water when...

11:07.577 --> 11:11.212
an elderly R-Rastafarian
hang glider...

11:11.214 --> 11:13.664
he-he crash
onto a beached squid,

11:13.666 --> 11:17.751
