(R&B music playing)
♪ Bang bang

20:32.360 --> 20:34.194
♪ Bangity bang
Um, Barney?

20:34.196 --> 20:36.746
Is this your way
of saying you're supporting us?

20:36.748 --> 20:38.398
BARNEY:
Yes! Go for it.

20:38.400 --> 20:40.950
♪ I said bang
Consummate your love!

20:40.952 --> 20:42.619
♪ Bang
Thanks, bro.

20:42.621 --> 20:46.456
